# Summary
This documentation details the Sleekflow destination integration for Amplitude, which enables syncing user cohorts to Sleekflow's omni-channel messaging platform for targeted communications via WhatsApp, Facebook Messenger, and other channels, requiring an email address or phone number as the unique identifier.

